text: Reşat Erceş (born 5 June 1918, date of death unknown) was a Turkish alpine skier. He competed in the men's combined event at the 1936 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1918 births Category:Year of death missing Category:Turkish male alpine skiers Category:Turkish male cross-country skiers Category:Olympic alpine skiers of Turkey Category:Olympic cross-country skiers of Turkey Category:Alpine skiers at the 1936 Winter Olympics Category:Cross- country skiers at the 1936 Winter Olympics Category:Place of birth missing
